Package simpleRugby.model

Class Member

java.lang.Object
simpleRugby.model.Member
Direct Known Subclasses:
Coach, Player, Staff
public class Member extends Object
Represents a general member of the rugby club. This can be a player, coach, or any other type of staff. Holds basic personal details and membership info.
